  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on the most absurd spacewalk of your life as a crew up to 8 unlucky souls, drifting through the chaotic void of space.    </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>    Explore  asteroid biomes and scavenge to pay your debt</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge space to collect debris with the grab and throw feature, and pay your debt to the Galactic Confederation. You'll be able to discover up to 20 levels including special event missions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cooperate… Or not</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can go outside by yourself, but you'll survive longer if find up to 7 other crew members and coordinate yourselves with proximity chat. Or you can just throw them on aliens, it's good fun too.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/7f80bf176faef0b42d99f9e6faa049f2.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/7f80bf176faef0b42d99f9e6faa049f2.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/7f80bf176faef0b42d99f9e6faa049f2.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fast play sessions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You only have 5 minutes to bring enough debris and repay the Galactic Confederation. Make sure your time is not shorted by excruciating death! Use your jetpack to explore these places and avoid their dangers. </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/ac3f39a91f95961a96983a4c73a986f4.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/ac3f39a91f95961a96983a4c73a986f4.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/ac3f39a91f95961a96983a4c73a986f4.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>    Upgrade your equipement to explore riskier zones</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Better jetpack, emergency kit, teleporter… Spend your supplies at the Scrapper HQ to prepare your crew. The more you succeed in missions, the more you’ll be able to spend and explore very hostile areas.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/be7246b18ddd6ceac1bcb967af8ca7ac.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/be7246b18ddd6ceac1bcb967af8ca7ac.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/be7246b18ddd6ceac1bcb967af8ca7ac.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>    Customize your suit with accessories and skins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You won’t be more efficient, but you’ll definitely be the coolest anglernaut of the crew. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/0915a1363520090ece6075d6f1f469af.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/0915a1363520090ece6075d6f1f469af.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/0915a1363520090ece6075d6f1f469af.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Up to 8 player online co-op</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Proximity voice chat</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Grab and throw items ability</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Procedurally generated maps</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Stuff upgrade between missions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Anglernaut customization</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>   Sense of Emergency and a few jump scares</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on the most absurd spacewalk of your life as a crew up to 8 unlucky souls, drifting through the chaotic void of space.    </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>    Explore  asteroid biomes and scavenge to pay your debt</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge space to collect debris with the grab and throw feature, and pay your debt to the Galactic Confederation. You'll be able to discover up to 20 levels including special event missions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/16f0b03e679dba50cb225962aba224e5.mp4?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cooperate… Or not</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can go outside by yourself, but you'll survive longer if find up to 7 other crew members and coordinate yourselves with proximity chat. Or you can just throw them on aliens, it's good fun too.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/7f80bf176faef0b42d99f9e6faa049f2.poster.avif?t=1734527950\" width=450 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230270/extras/7f80bf176faef0b42d99f9e6faa049f2.webm?t=1734527950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams